name: CJs
description:
Introduction

This canyon is described in limited detail in Canyons Near Sydney by Rick Jamieson. Help the Australian canyoning community by contributing track notes to ropewiki.com

Approach

Descent

Exit

Red tape

Beta sites

Trip reports and media

Background

The canyon name and grid reference was allegedly provided to guidebook author Rick Jamieson during the feud with guidebook author "SUBW" Dave Noble. Another canyon supplied was PJ's canyon which was intended to mean "Prick Jamieson". CJ's was far more vulgar.
